# ArchiStudio — Environment Variables

# Required: Supabase project credentials
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# Required: Site URL (used in SEO meta, sitemaps, JSON-LD schemas)
# Change this to your actual domain for production
VITE_SITE_URL=https://archistudio.shop

# Optional: Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# Optional: Cashfree Payment Gateway
# Mode is controlled in src/hooks/useCashfreePayment.ts
# Ensure the Edge Function create-cashfree-order uses production keys

# Notes:
# - Never commit your actual .env file to git
# - Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# - All VITE_ prefixed variables are exposed to the browser bundle
# - Sensitive keys (Cashfree secret, Supabase service role key) must ONLY
#   be used in Supabase Edge Functions, never in frontend code
